      "content": "i know about the hotlines, but it feels like just a bandaid on a wound that isn't going to heal. i'm not asking for a therapist, i'm asking if there's any actual logic to just stopping. like, if everything is just pain and there's no light at the end, isn't opting out a rational thing to consider?",
